episodes.title: The Wild Hunt
episodes.plot: A fierce creature is terrorizing the Candy Kingdom but before Finn can slay the beast, he must first overcome a guilty conscience.

episodes.title: Always BMO Closing
episodes.plot: BMO and Ice King hit the road as door-to-door salesmen and stumble upon an irresistible opportunity.

episodes.title: Son of Rap Bear
episodes.plot: When Flame Princess is coaxed into a high stakes battle against the indomitable Son of Rap Bear, Finn must help her search for a new strategy.

episodes.title: Bonnibel Bubblegum
episodes.plot: A long lost artifact causes Princess Bubblegum to go back to the creation of the Candy Kingdom.

episodes.title: Seventeen
episodes.plot: A mysterious knight crashes Finn's birthday bash and presents him with a dangerous gift.

episodes.title: Ring of Fire
episodes.plot: When an old flame comes calling on urgent business, Tree Trunks reconsiders both her wild past and her tranquil present.

episodes.title: Marcy & Hunson
episodes.plot: After helping with the creation of a new sword, Hunson Abadeer comes back to try and regain his daughter's love.

episodes.title: The First Investigation
episodes.plot: Finn and Jake are tasked with investigating reports of a haunting at Joshua and Margaret's old office.

episodes.title: Blenanas
episodes.plot: Finn's latest literary work meets with only derision, so he sets out to prove all the naysayers wrong.

episodes.title: Jake the Starchild
episodes.plot: In order to fulfill his grand destiny, Jake is spirited away by a strangely familiar shape-shifting alien.

episodes.title: Temple of Mars
episodes.plot: Searching for answers on Mars, Finn and Jermaine discover that they must first survive a cunning Martian mental trap.

episodes.title: Gumbaldia
episodes.plot: Finn and Jake, as ambassadors of the Candy Kingdom, travel to a powerful new city-state in a last ditch effort to stave off war.

episodes.title: Come Along With Me
episodes.plot: BMO narrates "The Great Gum War" in which Finn, Jake, Marceline, PB and the Candy Kingdom go to war against Gumbald and his army that will determine the fate of Ooo once and for all.
